FILE: README.md
================================================
# React + Tailwind

This template provides a minimal setup to get React working in Vite with HMR and some ESLint rules. One top of the standard Vite setup, [tailwindcss](https://tailwindcss.com/) is installed and ready to be used in React components.

Additional references:
* [Getting started with Vite](https://vitejs.dev/guide/)
* [Tailwind documentation](https://tailwindcss.com/docs/installation)

<soapenv:Envelope 
    xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/"
    xmlns:mat="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/service/matrikkelenhet"
    xmlns:mid="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/matrikkelenhet"
    xmlns:dom="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain"
    xmlns:kom="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kommune">
  <soapenv:Header/>
  <soapenv:Body>
    <mat:findMatrikkelenheter>
      <mat:matrikkelenhetsokModel>
        <!-- Riktig: direkte kommunenummer, ingen wrapper -->
        <mid:kommunenummer>0301</mid:kommunenummer>
        <mid:status>BESTAENDE</mid:status>
        <mid:gardsnummer>72</mid:gardsnummer>
        <mid:bruksnummer>94</mid:bruksnummer>
      </mat:matrikkelenhetsokModel>
      <mat:matrikkelContext>
        <dom:locale>no_NO_B</dom:locale>
        <dom:brukOriginaleKoordinater>false</dom:brukOriginaleKoordinater>
        <dom:koordinatsystemKodeId>
          <dom:value>25833</dom:value>
        </dom:koordinatsystemKodeId>
        <dom:systemVersion>trunk</dom:systemVersion>
        <dom:klientIdentifikasjon>proxy</dom:klientIdentifikasjon>
        <dom:snapshotVersion>
          <dom:timestamp>9999-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</dom:timestamp>
        </dom:snapshotVersion>
      </mat:matrikkelContext>
    </mat:findMatrikkelenheter>
  </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>

================================================
FILE: scripts/testMatrikkel.cjs
================================================
require('dotenv').config();
const soap = require('soap');

const wsdlUrl   = process.env.MATRIKKEL_WSDL;
const username  = process.env.MATRIKKEL_USER;
const password  = process.env.MATRIKKEL_PASS;
const endpoint  = process.env.MATRIKKEL_ENDPOINT; // Endpoint URL for the service, e.g. https://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/service/adresse

async function createClient() {
  // Hent og parse WSDL (med Basic Auth for nedlasting)
  const client = await soap.createClientAsync(wsdlUrl, {
    wsdl_options: { auth: `${username}:${password}` }
  });
  // Sett HTTP Basic Auth på alle kommende SOAP-kall
  client.setSecurity(new soap.BasicAuthSecurity(username, password));
  // Overskriv WSDL-ens address-lokasjon med den faktiske endpoint-URL
  client.setEndpoint(endpoint);
  return client;
}

async function logOperations() {
  const client = await createClient();
  console.log('Tjenester og metoder:');
  const desc = client.describe();
  for (const service of Object.keys(desc)) {
    for (const port of Object.keys(desc[service])) {
      console.log(`\n${service} → ${port}`);
      Object.keys(desc[service][port]).forEach(method => console.log(`  - ${method}`));
    }
  }
}

async function testAdresseKall() {
  try {
    const client = await createClient();
    const ident           = '0123456789';
    const snapshotVersion = '9999-01-01T00:00:00';

    const [res] = await client.findAdresseIdForIdentAsync({ ident, snapshotVersion });
    console.log('\nfindAdresseIdForIdent:', res);

    if (res.adresseId) {
      const [obj] = await client.getObjectAsync({ adresseId: res.adresseId, snapshotVersion });
      console.log('\ngetObject (adresse):');
      Object.entries(obj).forEach(([key, value]) =>
        console.log(`  • ${key}: ${typeof value}`)
      );
    }
  } catch (err) {
    console.error('Feil under testAdresseKall:', err);
  }
}

(async () => {
  try {
    await logOperations();
    await testAdresseKall();
  } catch (err) {
    console.error('Feil under API-test:', err);
  }
})();

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<xs:schema
    version="1.0"
    targetNamespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/adresse"
    xmlns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/adresse"
    xmlns:adressekoderns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/adresse/koder"
    xmlns:basistyperns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain"
    xmlns:bygningns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/bygning"
    xmlns:geometrins="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri"
    xmlns:kommunens="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kommune"
    xmlns:kommunetilleggns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kommunetillegg"
    xmlns:matrikkelenhetns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/matrikkelenhet"
    xmlns:personns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/person"
    xmlns:utilns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/util"
    xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" elementFormDefault="qualified">

    <xs:import schemaLocation="adresseKoder.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/adresse/koder"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="basistyper.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="bygning.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/bygning"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="geometri.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="kommune.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kommune"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="kommunetillegg.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kommunetillegg"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="matrikkelenhet.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/matrikkelenhet"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="person.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/person"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="util.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/util"/>


    <xs:complexType name="Adresse">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleObjectWithHistory">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="representasjonspunkt" type="geometrins:Representasjonspunkt"
                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="adressetilleggsnavn" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="kortnavn" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="matrikkelenhetId" type="matrikkelenhetns:MatrikkelenhetId"
                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="atkomster" type="AtkomstList" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="kretsIds" type="KretsIdList" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="kommunalTilleggsdel" type="kommunetilleggns:AdresseTillegg"
                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="tilleggsnavnKildeKodeId"
                                type="adressekoderns:AdressetilleggsnavnKildeKodeId"
                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="uuid" type="basistyperns:UUID" minOccurs="0">
                        <xs:annotation>
                            <xs:documentation>
                                Dette elementet gis kun ut for klientversjon 3.17 eller senere. For eldre klienter
                                returneres ikke dette elementet.
                                @since 3.17
                            </xs:documentation>
                        </xs:annotation>
                    </xs:element>
                </xs:sequence>
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="AdresseId">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleId">
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="AdresseIdList">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element name="item" nillable="true" type="AdresseId" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="AdresseIdent" abstract="true">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:Ident">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="kommuneIdent" type="kommunens:KommuneIdent"/>
                </xs:sequence>
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="AdresseIdentList">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element name="item" nillable="true" type="AdresseIdent" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>


    <xs:complexType name="Atkomst">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelComponentWithHistory">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="id" type="xs:long" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="opphavKodeId" type="adressekoderns:OpphavKodeId"
                                minOccurs="0"/>

                                minOccurs="0"/>

                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="uuid" type="basistyperns:UUID" minOccurs="0">
                        <xs:annotation>
                            <xs:documentation>
                                Dette elementet gis kun ut for klientversjon 4.1 eller senere. For eldre klienter
                                returneres ikke dette elementet.
                                @since 4.1
                            </xs:documentation>
                        </xs:annotation>
                    </xs:element>
                </xs:sequence>
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="AtkomstList">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded" name="item" nillable="true" type="Atkomst"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>


    <xs:complexType name="AdressemerkeBestilling">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleObject">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="bruksenhetId" type="bygningns:BruksenhetId" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="mottakersNavn" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="mottakersAdresse" type="personns:MottakerAdresse" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="utsattTilDato" type="basistyperns:Timestamp" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="bestiltDato" type="basistyperns:Timestamp" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="sendtTilProduksjonDato" type="basistyperns:Timestamp" minOccurs="0"/>
                </xs:sequence>

      <xs:element name="return" type="xs:int"/>
    </xs:sequence>

    targetNamespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/aktivitetsliste/koder"

    elementFormDefault="qualified">

               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kodeliste"/>

            <xs:extension base="kodens:MatrikkelEnumKode"/>

    </xs:complexType>

            <xs:extension base="kodens:MatrikkelEnumKode"/>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:simpleType name="ByggesakmeldingStatus">
        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
            <xs:enumeration value="MOTTATT"/>
            <xs:enumeration value="FERDIG"/>
            <xs:enumeration value="KVITTERT"/>
            <xs:enumeration value="ERROR"/>
        </xs:restriction>
    </xs:simpleType>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<xs:schema
    version="1.0"
    targetNamespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain"
    xmlns:basistyperns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain"
    xmlns:geometrikoderns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri/koder"
    xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema"
    elementFormDefault="qualified">

    <xs:import schemaLocation="geometriKoder.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri/koder"/>
    <!-- ================================================= -->
    <!-- Basisklasser                                      -->
    <!-- ================================================= -->
    <xs:complexType name="Timestamp">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element name="timestamp" type="xs:dateTime"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="LocalDate">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element name="date" type="xs:date"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="MatrikkelComponentWithHistory">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelComponent">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="oppdateringsdato" type="basistyperns:Timestamp" nillable="true"/>
                    <xs:element name="sluttdato" type="basistyperns:Timestamp" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="versjonId" type="xs:long"/>
                    <xs:element name="oppdatertAv" type="xs:string" nillable="true"/>
                    <xs:element name="avsluttetAv" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                </xs:sequence>
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="MatrikkelComponent">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element name="metadata" type="basistyperns:Metadata" minOccurs="0"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="MatrikkelBubbleId">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element name="value" type="xs:long"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded" name="item" nillable="true" type="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleId"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

                    xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/2003/10/Serialization/">
                    true
                </IsDictionary>
            </xs:appinfo>
        </xs:annotation>

            <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded" name="entry" nillable="true">
                <xs:complexType>
                    <xs:sequence>
                        <xs:element name="key" nillable="true" type="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleId"/>
                        <xs:element name="value" nillable="true" type="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleIdList"/>
                    </xs:sequence>
                </xs:complexType>
            </xs:element>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

            </xs:appinfo>
        </xs:annotation>

                    <xs:sequence>
                        <xs:element name="key" type="basistyperns:Timestamp"/>
                        <xs:element name="value" type="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleId"/>
                    </xs:sequence>
                </xs:complexType>
            </xs:element>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="MatrikkelBubbleIdToMatrikkelBubbleObjectMap">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:appinfo>
                <IsDictionary
                    xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/2003/10/Serialization/">
                    true
                </IsDictionary>
            </xs:appinfo>
        </xs:annotation>

            </xs:element>

    </xs:complexType>

        </xs:annotation>

        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="UUID">
        <xs:annotation>

               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kommune"/>

            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleObjectWithHistory">

                    <xs:element name="adresse" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="postadresse" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="epost" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="telefonnummer" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="endrePassordVedInnlogging" type="xs:boolean" minOccurs="0"/>

                    <xs:element name="snappetoleranse" type="xs:double" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="standardStiForBakgrunnskart" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="aktuellKommuneId" type="kommunens:KommuneId" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="brukStoreKnapper" type="xs:boolean" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="dataForWMSer" type="DataForWMSList" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="ndBruker" type="xs:boolean" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="baatBruker" type="xs:boolean" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="opprettetAvId" type="BrukerId" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="opprettetDato" type="basistyperns:Timestamp" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="adgangSlettetAvId" type="BrukerId" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="adgangSlettetDato" type="basistyperns:Timestamp" minOccurs="0"/>

                </xs:sequence>
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="brukerId" type="ns4:BrukerId"/>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns2:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="harLesFodselsnummerRettighetResponse">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="return" type="xs:boolean"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns2:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="return" type="ns4:BrukerIdentTilBrukerIdMap"/>

<xs:schema
    xmlns:bygningkoderns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/bygning/koder"

    xmlns:geometrins="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri"

    xmlns:matrikkelenhetns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/matrikkelenhet"
    xmlns:kommunetilleggns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kommunetillegg"
    xmlns:utilns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/util"
    xmlns:sefrak="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/sefrak"
    xmlns:kulturminne="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kulturminne"
    xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema"
    version="1.0"
    targetNamespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/bygning"
    xmlns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/bygning"

      <xs:element name="id" nillable="true" type="ns3:MatrikkelEndringId"/>
      <xs:element name="domainklasse" type="ns3:Domainklasse"/>
      <xs:element name="filter" nillable="true" type="xs:string"/>
      <xs:element name="returnerBobler" type="ns3:ReturnerBobler"/>
      <xs:element name="maksAntall" type="xs:int"/>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns2:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="findEndringerResponse">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="return" type="ns3:Endringer"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>
</xs:schema>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<xs:schema
    version="1.0"
    elementFormDefault="qualified"
    targetNamespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/exception"
    xmlns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/exception"
    xmlns:basistyperns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain"
    xmlns:geometrins="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri"
    xmlns:elektronisktinglysning="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/elektronisktinglysing"
    xmlns:geometrikoderns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri/koder"
    xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema"
    xmlns:jaxb="https://jakarta.ee/xml/ns/jaxb"
    jaxb:version="3.0"
>

    <xs:import schemaLocation="basistyper.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="geometri.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="elektronisktinglysing.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/elektronisktinglysing"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="geometriKoder.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri/koder"/>

    <!-- ========================================================= -->
    <!-- Exception:                                                -->
    <!-- Skjema for å mappe exception (med stacktrace)             -->
    <!-- ========================================================= -->

    <xs:annotation>
        <xs:appinfo>
            <jaxb:schemaBindings>
                <jaxb:package>
                    <jaxb:javadoc><![CDATA[
                        <body>Denne pakken inneholder navn og typer for feil og feiltyper som kan oppstå i API-et.</body>
                    ]]></jaxb:javadoc>
                </jaxb:package>
            </jaxb:schemaBindings>
        </xs:appinfo>
    </xs:annotation>

    <!-- .NET fix -->
    <!-- Elements definition must be hand written and introduced here in order for .NET datacontract generating to work... -->
    <xs:element name="ServiceException" nillable="true" type="ServiceFaultInfo"/>
    <!-- .NET end -->


    <xs:complexType name="ServiceFaultInfo">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:appinfo>
                <jaxb:class>
                    <jaxb:javadoc><![CDATA[
                        Generell feilmelding for alle hånterte feil ifra systemet.

                        Alle feil har en utfyllt feilkode og feilkodebeskrivelse.

                        For klassifisering av feil, se {@link #category} feltet.
                    ]]></jaxb:javadoc>
                </jaxb:class>
            </xs:appinfo>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element name="category" type="xs:string">
                <xs:annotation>
                    <xs:appinfo>
                        <jaxb:property>
                            <jaxb:javadoc>
                                <![CDATA[
                                Kategorisering av feil. Her blir hver supertype av exceptionklasser lagt til i en kolon-separert liste.
                                Det siste leddet annoterer da konkret subtype av exception.

                                <br>
                                En eksempelimplementasjon kan ønske å skille systemfeil ifra applikasjonsfeil. Dette gjøres enkelt ved å matche {@link #category}-streng mot ":SystemException:" osv..

                                <p>
                                Kategorisering av feil skjer etter følgende struktur:
                                <ul style="list-style-type: circle">
                                  <li>
                                    <b>ServiceException</b>
                                    verdi = {@code ":ServiceException:"}
                                    <ul>
                                      <li>
                                        <b>SystemException</b>
                                        verdi = {@code ":ServiceException:SystemException:"}
                                        <br>
                                            Felles klasse for alle typer systemfeil. <br />
                                            Systemfeil skiller seg ifra applikasjonsfeil på den måte da dette er feil som oppstår i og ved kjøring av miljøet som applikasjonen kjører i.
                                            Eksempler er implementasjonsfeil og feil som kan oppstå når deler av det fysiske miljøet rundt ikke er tilgjengelig.
                                        <ul>
                                          <li>
                                            <b>ImplementationException</b>
                                            verdi = {@code ":ServiceException:SystemException:ImplementationException:"}
                                            <br>
                                                Feil som oppstår i kode enten på server, eller på bagrunn av feil i kall fra klient.
                                          </li>
                                          <li>
                                            <b>OperationalException</b>
                                            verdi = {@code ":ServiceException:SystemException:OperationalException:"}
                                            <br>
                                                Operasjonelle feil har feilkilder som stammer utelukkende ifra det utenpåliggende miljøet systemet kjører i.
                                                Typiske eksempler er at serveren går tom for diskplass, eller at forbindelsen med databasen blir borte.
                                          </li>
                                        </ul>
                                      </li>
                                      <li>
                                        <b>ApplicationException</b>
                                        verdi = {@code ":ServiceException:ApplicationException:"}
                                        <br>
                                            Felles type for alle applikasjonsfeil.
                                            Applikasjonsfeil skiller seg ifra systemfeil på den måte da dette er feil som direkte skyldes applikasjons-spesifik logikk og validering.
                                            Med dette forstås brukerfeil så vel som domeneregler applikasjonen definerer.
                                        <ul>
                                          <li>
                                            <b>FinderException</b>
                                            verdi = {@code ":ServiceException:ApplicationException:FinderException:"}
                                            <br>
                                                Felles klasse for feil ved oppslag der datagrunnlag ikke finnes i henhold til gitte kriterier.
                                          </li>
                                          <li>
                                            <b>ValidationException</b>
                                            verdi = {@code ":ServiceException:ApplicationException:ValidationException:"}
                                            <br>
                                                Felles klasse for feil ved validering der datagrunnlag ikke er i henhold til spesifiserte regler.
                                          </li>
                                        </ul>
                                      </li>
                                    </ul>
                                  </li>
                                </ul>
                            ]]></jaxb:javadoc>
                        </jaxb:property>
                    </xs:appinfo>
                </xs:annotation>
            </xs:element>
            <xs:element name="stackTraceText" type="xs:string">
                <xs:annotation>
                    <xs:appinfo>
                        <jaxb:property>
                            <jaxb:javadoc>
                                <![CDATA[Formatert, komplett, stacktrace som kan innrapporteres. Denne er kun brukt ved {@link SystemException systemfeil}.]]></jaxb:javadoc>
                        </jaxb:property>
                    </xs:appinfo>
                </xs:annotation>
            </xs:element>
            <xs:element name="exceptionDetail" type="ExceptionDetail">
                <xs:annotation>
                    <xs:appinfo>
                        <jaxb:property>
                            <jaxb:javadoc><![CDATA[Maskinlesbar informasjon om exception.]]></jaxb:javadoc>
                        </jaxb:property>
                    </xs:appinfo>
                </xs:annotation>
            </xs:element>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="ExceptionDetail">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:appinfo>
                <jaxb:class>
                    <jaxb:javadoc>
                        <![CDATA[Informasjon om exception oppstått på server med hirarki, stacktrace mm.]]></jaxb:javadoc>
                </jaxb:class>
            </xs:appinfo>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element name="className" type="xs:string">
                <xs:annotation>
                    <xs:appinfo>
                        <jaxb:property>
                            <jaxb:javadoc><![CDATA[Klassenavn for exception.]]></jaxb:javadoc>
                        </jaxb:property>
                    </xs:appinfo>
                </xs:annotation>
            </xs:element>
            <xs:element name="message" type="xs:string">
                <xs:annotation>
                    <xs:appinfo>
                        <jaxb:property>
                            <jaxb:javadoc><![CDATA[Teknisk underliggende feilmeldingstekst.]]></jaxb:javadoc>
                        </jaxb:property>
                    </xs:appinfo>
                </xs:annotation>
            </xs:element>
            <xs:element name="cause" type="ExceptionDetail" nillable="true">
                <xs:annotation>
                    <xs:appinfo>
                        <jaxb:property>
                            <jaxb:javadoc><![CDATA[Evt nøstet exception kan komme her.]]></jaxb:javadoc>
                        </jaxb:property>
                    </xs:appinfo>
                </xs:annotation>
            </xs:element>
            <xs:element name="stackTraceElements" type="StackTraceElementList">
                <xs:annotation>
                    <xs:appinfo>
                        <jaxb:property>
                            <jaxb:javadoc>
                                <![CDATA[Stacktrace generert ifra system. Denne er kun brukt ved {@link SystemException systemfeil}.]]></jaxb:javadoc>
                        </jaxb:property>
                    </xs:appinfo>
                </xs:annotation>
            </xs:element>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="StackTraceElementList">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:appinfo>
                <jaxb:class>
                    <jaxb:javadoc><![CDATA[ ]]></jaxb:javadoc>
                </jaxb:class>
            </xs:appinfo>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element name="item" nillable="true" type="StackTraceElement" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="StackTraceElement">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:appinfo>
                <jaxb:class>
                    <jaxb:javadoc><![CDATA[ ]]></jaxb:javadoc>
                </jaxb:class>
            </xs:appinfo>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element name="declaringClass" type="xs:string"/>
            <xs:element name="methodName" type="xs:string"/>
            <xs:element name="fileName" type="xs:string" nillable="true"/>
            <xs:element name="lineNumber" type="xs:int"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="LockedFaultInfo">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="ServiceFaultInfo">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="locksNotAquired" type="LockNotAquiredList"/>

    elementFormDefault="qualified">

    <xs:import schemaLocation="basistyper.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain"/>

               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri/koder"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="matrikkelenhet.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/matrikkelenhet"/>


    <xs:complexType name="AnleggsprojeksjonsArc">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="AnleggsprojeksjonsCurveSegment">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="buepunkt" type="Position" minOccurs="1"/>
                </xs:sequence>
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>


    <xs:complexType name="AnleggsprojeksjonsBoundary">

                    <xs:element name="uuid" type="basistyperns:UUID" minOccurs="0">
                        <xs:annotation>
                            <xs:documentation>
                                Dette elementet gis kun ut for klientversjon 3.17 eller senere. For eldre klienter
                                returneres ikke dette elementet.
                                @since 3.17

                    </xs:element>

    </xs:complexType>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<xs:schema
    version="1.0"
    targetNamespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri/koder"
    xmlns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri/koder"
    xmlns:kodens="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kodeliste"
    xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema"
    elementFormDefault="qualified">

    <xs:import schemaLocation="kodeliste.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kodeliste"/>


    <xs:complexType name="KoordinatkvalitetKode">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="kodens:MatrikkelEnumKode"/>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="KoordinatkvalitetKodeId">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="kodens:MatrikkelEnumKodeId"/>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="KoordinatkvalitetKodeIdList">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element name="item" nillable="true" type="KoordinatkvalitetKodeId" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>


    <xs:complexType name="KoordinatsystemKode">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="kodens:MatrikkelEnumKode">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="sosiKode" type="xs:int" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="epsgKode" type="xs:int" minOccurs="0"/>
                </xs:sequence>

    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="findGrunnforurensingerForMatrikkelenhet">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelenhetId" type="ns1:MatrikkelenhetId"/>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns3:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="findGrunnforurensingerForMatrikkelenhetResponse">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="return" type="ns4:GrunnforurensingIdList"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>
</xs:schema>

    version="1.0"
    targetNamespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/jobb"
    xmlns:basistyperns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain"

    xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" elementFormDefault="qualified">

               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="bruker.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/bruker"/>

               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/jobb/koder"/>

               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kodeliste"/>

        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleObject">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="brukerId" type="brukerns:BrukerId" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="typeId" type="JobbtypeKodeId" minOccurs="0"/>

                    <xs:element name="oppgaveId" type="JobbOppgaveId" minOccurs="0"/>
                </xs:sequence>
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleId"/>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

            <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded" name="item" nillable="true" type="JobbId"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:sequence>

            </xs:element>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><xs:schema xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:ns1="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri/koder" xmlns:ns2="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain" xmlns:ns3="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kodeliste" xmlns:tns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/service/kodeliste" elementFormDefault="qualified" targetNamespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/service/kodeliste" version="1.0">

  <xs:import namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri/koder" schemaLocation="geometriKoder.xsd"/>

  <xs:import namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain" schemaLocation="basistyper.xsd"/>

  <xs:import namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kodeliste" schemaLocation="kodeliste.xsd"/>

  <xs:element name="getKodelister" type="tns:getKodelister"/>

  <xs:element name="getKodelisterEnkel" type="tns:getKodelisterEnkel"/>

  <xs:element name="getKodelisterEnkelResponse" type="tns:getKodelisterEnkelResponse"/>

  <xs:element name="getKodelisterResponse" type="tns:getKodelisterResponse"/>

  <xs:complexType name="getKodelisterEnkel">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns2:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="getKodelisterEnkelResponse">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="return" type="ns3:KodelisteTransfer"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="getKodelister">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="snapshotVersion" type="ns2:Timestamp"/>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns2:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="getKodelisterResponse">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="return" type="ns3:KodelisteTransfer"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>
</xs:schema>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<xs:schema
    version="1.0"
    targetNamespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kommune"
    xmlns:kommunens="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kommune"
    xmlns:brukerkoderns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/bruker/koder"
    xmlns:basistyperns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain"
    xmlns:geometrins="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri"
    xmlns:geometrikoderns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri/koder"
    xmlns:personns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/person"
    xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" elementFormDefault="qualified">

    <xs:import schemaLocation="brukerKoder.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/bruker/koder"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="basistyper.xsd" namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="geometri.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="geometriKoder.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri/koder"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="person.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/person"/>


    <xs:complexType name="KommuneId">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleId">
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="KommuneIdList">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded" name="item" type="kommunens:KommuneId" nillable="true"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="StringTilKommuneIdMap">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:appinfo>
                <IsDictionary
                    xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/2003/10/Serialization/">
                    true
                </IsDictionary>
            </xs:appinfo>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded" name="entry" nillable="true">
                <xs:complexType>
                    <xs:sequence>
                        <xs:element name="key" nillable="true" type="xs:string"/>
                        <xs:element name="value" nillable="true" type="kommunens:KommuneId"/>
                    </xs:sequence>
                </xs:complexType>
            </xs:element>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="StringTilKommuneIdListMap">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:appinfo>
                <IsDictionary
                    xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/2003/10/Serialization/">
                    true
                </IsDictionary>
            </xs:appinfo>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded" name="entry" nillable="true">
                <xs:complexType>
                    <xs:sequence>
                        <xs:element name="key" nillable="true" type="xs:string"/>
                        <xs:element name="value" type="kommunens:KommuneIdList"/>
                    </xs:sequence>
                </xs:complexType>
            </xs:element>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="KommuneIdent">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:Ident">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="kommunenummer" type="xs:string"/>
                </xs:sequence>
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="KommuneIdentList">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded" name="item" type="kommunens:KommuneIdent" nillable="true"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="Kommune">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleObjectWithHistory">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="kommunenummer" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="kommunenavn" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="fylkeId" type="kommunens:FylkeId" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="gyldigTilDato" type="basistyperns:LocalDate" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="nyKommuneId" type="kommunens:KommuneId" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="koordinatsystemKodeId" type="geometrikoderns:KoordinatsystemKodeId"
                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="konverteringStatus" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="last" type="xs:boolean" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="senterpunkt" type="geometrins:Position" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="representasjonspunkt" type="geometrins:Representasjonspunkt"
                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="postadresse" type="personns:MottakerAdresse" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="standardRekvirentTinglysingId" type="personns:JuridiskPersonId" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="sprakformId" type="brukerkoderns:SprakformId" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="naboKommuneIds" type="kommunens:KommuneIdList" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="eksklusivBruker" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="nedsattKonsesjonsgrense" type="xs:boolean" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="brukteGardsnummer" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="uuid" type="basistyperns:UUID" minOccurs="0">
                        <xs:annotation>
                            <xs:documentation>
                                Dette elementet gis kun ut for klientversjon 3.17 eller senere. For eldre klienter
                                returneres ikke dette elementet.
                                @since 3.17
                            </xs:documentation>
                        </xs:annotation>
                    </xs:element>
                </xs:sequence>
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><xs:schema xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:ns1="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kommune" xmlns:ns2="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri/koder" xmlns:ns3="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain" xmlns:tns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/service/kommune" elementFormDefault="qualified" targetNamespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/service/kommune" version="1.0">

                    <xs:element name="referanse" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                </xs:sequence>
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="VegReferanseList">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element name="item" nillable="true" type="VegReferanse" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>


    <xs:complexType name="VegTillegg">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelComponent">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="vegReferanser" type="VegReferanseList" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="kommentarer" type="KommentarList" minOccurs="0"/>
                </xs:sequence>
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

</xs:schema>

    xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema"
    elementFormDefault="qualified">


    <xs:import schemaLocation="basistyper.xsd" namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain"/>

    <xs:import schemaLocation="matrikkelenhet.xsd"

               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kodeliste"/>
    <xs:import schemaLocation="kulturminneKoder.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/kulturminne/koder"/>

    <xs:complexType name="FredetBygning">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelComponentWithHistory">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="id" type="xs:long" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="enkeltminnenummer" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="enkeltminneArtKodeId" type="kulturminnekoderns:EnkeltminneArtKodeId"
                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="vernetypeKodeId" type="kulturminnekoderns:VernetypeKodeId" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="kategoriKodeId" type="kulturminnekoderns:KulturminnekategoriKodeId"
                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="bygningId" type="bygningns:BygningId" minOccurs="0"/>
                </xs:sequence>
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="FredetBygningList">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded" name="item" nillable="true" type="FredetBygning"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="FredetBygningId">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleId"/>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="FredetBygningIdList">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded" name="item" nillable="true" type="FredetBygningId"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="Kulturminne">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleObjectWithHistory">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="lokalitetsnummer" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="kulturminneArtKodeId" type="kulturminnekoderns:KulturminneArtKodeId"
                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="vernetypeKodeId" type="kulturminnekoderns:VernetypeKodeId" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="kulturminnekategoriId" type="kulturminnekoderns:KulturminnekategoriKodeId"
                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="matrikkelforingsdato" type="basistyperns:LocalDate" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="sistOppdatertDato" type="basistyperns:LocalDate" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="matrikkelenhetIds" type="matrikkelenhetns:MatrikkelenhetIdList" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="enkeltminner" type="FredetBygningList" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="uuid" type="basistyperns:UUID" minOccurs="0">
                        <xs:annotation>
                            <xs:documentation>
                                Dette elementet gis kun ut for klientversjon 3.17 eller senere. For eldre klienter
                                returneres ikke dette elementet.
                                @since 3.17
                            </xs:documentation>
                        </xs:annotation>
                    </xs:element>
                </xs:sequence>
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="KulturminneId">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleId">
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><xs:schema xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:ns1="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain" xmlns:ns2="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri/koder" xmlns:tns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/service/lock" elementFormDefault="qualified" targetNamespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/service/lock" version="1.0">

  <xs:import namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain" schemaLocation="basistyper.xsd"/>

  <xs:import namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri/koder" schemaLocation="geometriKoder.xsd"/>

  <xs:element name="isLocked" type="tns:isLocked"/>

  <xs:element name="isLockedResponse" type="tns:isLockedResponse"/>

  <xs:element name="lock" type="tns:lock"/>

  <xs:element name="lockForList" type="tns:lockForList"/>

  <xs:element name="lockForListResponse" type="tns:lockForListResponse"/>

  <xs:element name="lockResponse" type="tns:lockResponse"/>

  <xs:element name="unlock" type="tns:unlock"/>

  <xs:element name="unlockForList" type="tns:unlockForList"/>

  <xs:element name="unlockForListResponse" type="tns:unlockForListResponse"/>

  <xs:element name="unlockResponse" type="tns:unlockResponse"/>

  <xs:complexType name="unlockForList">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="ids" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleIdList"/>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns1:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="unlockForListResponse">
    <xs:sequence/>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="isLocked">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="id" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleId"/>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns1:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="isLockedResponse">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="return" type="xs:boolean"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="unlock">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="id" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleId"/>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns1:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="unlockResponse">
    <xs:sequence/>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="lockForList">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="ids" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleIdList"/>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns1:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="lockForListResponse">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="return" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleObjectList"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="lock">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="id" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleId"/>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns1:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="lockResponse">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="return" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleObject"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>
</xs:schema>

    <xs:import schemaLocation="pantebok.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/pantebok"/>


    <xs:complexType name="Anleggseiendom">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="matrikkelenhetns:Matrikkelenhet">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="anleggstypeId" type="matrikkelenhetkoderns:AnleggstypeKodeId"
                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="anleggsprojeksjonsflaterForMatrikkelenhet"
                                type="matrikkelenhetns:AnleggsprojeksjonsflateForMatrikkelenhetList"

    </xs:complexType>

            <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded" name="item" nillable="true"
                        type="matrikkelenhetns:AnleggseiendomId"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

                        type="matrikkelenhetns:MatrikkelenhetBokInfo"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="Anleggsprojeksjonsflate">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:MatrikkelBubbleObjectWithHistory">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="lagretBeregnetAreal" type="xs:double" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="datafangstdato" type="basistyperns:LocalDate" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="kommentar" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="mediumId" type="matrikkelenhetkoderns:MediumId"
                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="flate" type="geometrins:AnleggsprojeksjonsComplexSurface"
                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="kommunalTilleggsdel"
                                type="kommunetilleggns:AnleggsprojeksjonsflateTillegg"
                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="representasjonspunkt" type="geometrins:Representasjonspunkt"
                                minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="oppgittVolum" type="xs:double" minOccurs="0"/>
                    <xs:element name="uuid" type="basistyperns:UUID" minOccurs="0">
                        <xs:annotation>
                            <xs:documentation>
                                Dette elementet gis kun ut for klientversjon 3.17 eller senere. For eldre klienter
                                returneres ikke dette elementet.
                                @since 3.17
                            </xs:documentation>
                        </xs:annotation>
                    </xs:element>
                </xs:sequence>
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>

    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="harHoveddokumentResponse">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="return" type="xs:boolean"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>
</xs:schema>

            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

            <xs:extension base="kodens:MatrikkelEnumKodeId"/>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

  <xs:import namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain" schemaLocation="basistyper.xsd"/>

  <xs:import namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/geometri/koder" schemaLocation="geometriKoder.xsd"/>

  <xs:element name="getObject" type="tns:getObject"/>

  <xs:element name="getObjectResponse" type="tns:getObjectResponse"/>

  <xs:element name="getObjects" type="tns:getObjects"/>

  <xs:element name="getObjectsIgnoreMissing" type="tns:getObjectsIgnoreMissing"/>

  <xs:element name="getObjectsIgnoreMissingResponse" type="tns:getObjectsIgnoreMissingResponse"/>

  <xs:element name="getObjectsResponse" type="tns:getObjectsResponse"/>

  <xs:element name="getVersions" type="tns:getVersions"/>

  <xs:element name="getVersionsForList" type="tns:getVersionsForList"/>

  <xs:element name="getVersionsForListResponse" type="tns:getVersionsForListResponse"/>

  <xs:element name="getVersionsResponse" type="tns:getVersionsResponse"/>

  <xs:complexType name="getObjectsIgnoreMissing">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="ids" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleIdList"/>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns1:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="getObjectsIgnoreMissingResponse">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="return" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleObjectList"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="getVersions">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="id" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleId"/>
      <xs:element name="start" type="ns1:Timestamp"/>
      <xs:element name="end" type="ns1:Timestamp"/>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns1:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="getVersionsResponse">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="return" type="ns1:SnapshotVersionToMatrikkelBubbleIdMap"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="getVersionsForList">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="ids" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleIdList"/>
      <xs:element name="start" type="ns1:Timestamp"/>
      <xs:element name="end" type="ns1:Timestamp"/>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns1:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="getVersionsForListResponse">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="return" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleIdToSnapshotBubbleIdsMap"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="getObjects">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="ids" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleIdList"/>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns1:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="getObjectsResponse">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="return" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleObjectList"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="getObject">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element name="id" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleId"/>
      <xs:element name="matrikkelContext" type="ns1:MatrikkelContext"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>

  <xs:complexType name="getObjectResponse">
    <xs:sequence>
      <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="return" type="ns1:MatrikkelBubbleObject"/>
    </xs:sequence>
  </xs:complexType>
</xs:schema>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<xs:schema
    version="1.0"
    targetNamespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/test"
    xmlns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/test"
    xmlns:basistyperns="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain"
    xmlns:test="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/test"
    xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema"
    elementFormDefault="qualified">

    <xs:import schemaLocation="basistyper.xsd"
               namespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain"/>

    <xs:complexType name="TestNumber">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element name="offset" type="xs:int"/>
            <xs:element name="number" type="xs:int"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="MatrikkelnummerList">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded" name="item" nillable="true" type="MatrikkelnummerDTO"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="MatrikkelnummerDTO">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element name="matrikkelenhetid" type="xs:long" minOccurs="0"/>
            <xs:element name="kommuneid" type="xs:long" minOccurs="0"/>
            <xs:element name="gardsnr" type="xs:int" minOccurs="0"/>
            <xs:element name="bruksnr" type="xs:int" minOccurs="0"/>
            <xs:element name="festenr" type="xs:int" minOccurs="0"/>
            <xs:element name="seksjonsnr" type="xs:int" minOccurs="0"/>
            <xs:element name="utgattmatrikkelnummer" type="test:UtgattMatrikkelnummerKode" minOccurs="0"/>
            <xs:element name="versjonid" type="xs:int" minOccurs="0"/>
            <xs:element name="oppdateringsdato" type="basistyperns:Timestamp" minOccurs="0"/>
            <xs:element name="sluttdato" type="basistyperns:Timestamp" minOccurs="0"/>
            <xs:element name="oppdatertAv" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
            <xs:element name="avsluttetAv" type="xs:string" minOccurs="0"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:simpleType name="UtgattMatrikkelnummerKode">
        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
            <xs:enumeration value="Aktiv"/>
            <xs:enumeration value="Utgatt"/>
            <xs:enumeration value="Reservert"/>
        </xs:restriction>
    </xs:simpleType>

    <xs:complexType name="MockupTransfer">
        <xs:complexContent>
            <xs:extension base="basistyperns:UnitOfWorkTransfer">
                <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="testNumber" type="TestNumber"/>
                </xs:sequence>
            </xs:extension>
        </xs:complexContent>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:complexType name="MockupSnapshotMap">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:appinfo>
                <IsDictionary
                    xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/2003/10/Serialization/">
                    true
                </IsDictionary>
            </xs:appinfo>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded" name="entry" nillable="true">
                <xs:complexType>
                    <xs:sequence>
                        <xs:element name="key" nillable="true" type="basistyperns:Timestamp"/>
                        <xs:element name="value" type="MockupTransfer"/>
                    </xs:sequence>
                </xs:complexType>
            </xs:element>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

</xs:schema>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<xs:schema
    version="1.0"
    targetNamespace="http://matrikkel.statkart.no/matrikkelapi/wsapi/v1/domain/util"
    xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema"
    elementFormDefault="qualified">

    <xs:complexType name="Andel">
        <xs:sequence>
            <xs:element name="teller" type="xs:long" minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1"/>
            <xs:element name="nevner" type="xs:long" minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1"/>
        </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>

    <xs:simpleType name="Interval">
        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
            <xs:pattern value="\s*\d+\s*(-\s*\d+)?\s*(,\s*\d+\s*(-\s*\d+)?)*"/>
        </xs:restriction>
    </xs:simpleType>

    <xs:simpleType name="Status">
        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
            <xs:enumeration value="BESTAENDE"/>
            <xs:enumeration value="UTGATTE"/>
        </xs:restriction>
    </xs:simpleType>

</xs:schema>
